OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear spells
OL,6,Fand scattered showers through the
OL,7,Fevening and overnight, these showers
OL,8,Fheavy and blustery at times.
OL,9,FOccasionally strong southwest winds,
OL,10,Fveering steadily westerly overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FBright spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers in the morning, showers
OL,14,Fbecoming less frequent in the
OL,15,Fafternoon allowing longer sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Strong winds at first easing
OL,17,Fby day. Cooler than recent days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
