OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCold
OL,6,Fstart on Saturday then bright spells
OL,7,Fand a few showers, these mainly in the
OL,8,Fwest. Cloudy and windier on Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday with further rain.
